+## Atomic Findings Extracted
+
+1. The tidy six-mode mirror-complete ledger is only a pseudo-survivor created
+   by truncating closure to the original triad orbit.
+2. The smallest admissible enlargement on `p - q` keeps the same search class
+   and still reproduces the first-budget spill through the same off-orbit
+   forcing.
